description: The relationship between Beres Hammond and VP Records dates to the late 1980s, with 10 albums released over 30 years. His commercial standout was Music Is Life, and 2021 marked a career highlight with the exceptional Love From A Distance virtual concert, which attracted more than 100,000 viewers.
